The paper also involves image datasets and computer vision tasks, which suggest the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also involves deep learning models and optimization techniques, which are typical topics in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
